verflow-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box;\">“我们听到了民众的声音，并且要去实现它。今天将是见证历史的一天，日后我们会为今天的决定所庆幸的。”</p><p style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box;\"><br/></p><p style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 192, 0);\"><strong style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box;\">素里房价面临大涨！</strong></span></p><p style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box;\"><br/></strong></p><p style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box;\"></strong></p><p style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box;\">在房市冷淡的日子里，素里的公寓销量却依旧坚挺，</p><p style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; box-sizing: border-box;\"/></p><p style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(255, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; box-sizing: border-box;\">背后支撑着素里销量的就是大型交通项目的兴建！</strong></span></p><p style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(255, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; box-sizing: border-box;\"/></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align:center;overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"http://cacnews.ca/data/attachment/portal/201811/07/093154k1jttpwfbft5y9bt.jpg\" alt=\"重磅！素里天车全票通过 直通兰里 房价将要涨疯！至少增值27% 特鲁多这样说……\" data-bd-imgshare-binded=\"1\" style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 620px;\"/></p><p style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; box-sizing: border-box;\"/></p><p style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box;\">地产界人士指出，由交通线带来的房价升值通常分三个阶段。</p><p style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word;\"/></p><p style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box;\"><br/></p><p style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; box-sizing: border-box;\">第一个阶段是概念阶段。</strong>项目计划刚出时，买房人通常会考虑未来交通线铺好后将迎来地产增值，因此会在交通沿线置业。&nbsp;<br style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; box-sizing: border-box;\"/></p><p style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; box-sizing: border-box;\"/></p><p style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; box-sizing: border-box;\">第二个阶段是落实阶段。</strong>项目已经在修建，此期间已购的物业升值的空间会比较小。&nbsp;<br style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; box-sizing: border-box;\"/></p><p style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; box-sizing: border-box;\"/></p><p style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; fon