ef=\"https://www.westca.com/House/articles/op=view_tag/tag=%B5%D8%B2%FA/lang=schinese.html?utm_source=westca&utm_medium=tag&utm_campaign=news_extend\" style=\";font-size: 14px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simhei, Georgia;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">地产</a><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simhei, Georgia;font-size: 14px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">市场开刀。</span><br style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simhei, Georgia;font-size: 14px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"/><br style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simhei, Georgia;font-size: 14px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"/><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simhei, Georgia;font-size: 14px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">温哥华市政府计划将城市的</span><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.westca.com/House/articles/op=view_tag/tag=%B7%BF%B5%D8%B2%FA/lang=schinese.html?utm_source=westca&utm_medium=tag&utm_campaign=news_extend\" style=\";font-size: 14px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simhei, Georgia;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">房地产</a><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simhei, Georgia;font-size: 14px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">税（Property Tax）自2019年开始提升至4.9%。在致BC省住房部长的信中，温哥华市长表示，额外的学校税“会影响温哥华市政税基”，并可能导致市政税收问题。</span><br style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simhei, Georgia;font-size: 14px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"/><br style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simhei, Georgia;font-size: 14px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"/><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simhei, Georgia;font-size: 14px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">作为NDP政府解决</span><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.westca.com/House/articles/op=view_tag/tag=%B7%BF%CA%D0/lang=schinese.html?utm_source=westca&utm_medium=tag&utm_campaign=news_extend\" style=\";font-size: 14px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simhei, Georgia;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">房市</a><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simhei, Georgia;font-size: 14px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">危机的一项政策之一，学校税原计划将于2019年开始实行。然而，温哥华市政府为民谋福利，投票要取消它！</span></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simhei, Georgia;font-size: 14px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><img src=\"http://img2.westca.com/uploads/201812/51775432.jpg\" style=\"max-width: 660px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simhei, Georgia;font-size: 14px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"/><br style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simhei, Georgia;font-size: 14px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"/><br style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simhei, Georgia;font-size: 14px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"/><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simhei, Georgia;font-size: 14px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">学校税，是指对</span><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.westca.com/House/articles/op=view_tag/tag=%B7%BF%CE%DD/lang=schinese.html?utm_source=westca&utm_medium=tag&utm_campaign=news_extend\" style=\";font-size: 14px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simhei, Georgia;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">房屋</a><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simhei, Georgia;font-size: 14px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">评估价值在300万-400万之间的收取评估值的0.2%、对于估值400万以上的收0.4%的房屋价值作为学校税。</span><br style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simhei, Georgia;font-size: 14px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"/><br style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simhei, Georgia;font-size: 14px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"/><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simhei, Georgia;font-size: 14px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">也就是说原本评估值350万的房屋，除去地税之外，还需额外缴纳7000元作为学校税。</span></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simhei, Georgia;font-size: 14px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simhei, Georgia;font-size: 14px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20181219/1545178271685729.jpg\" title=\"1545178271685729.jpg\" alt=\"536c4b414.jpg\"/></span></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simhei, Georgia;font-size: 14px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simhei, Georgia;font-size: 14px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simhei, Georgia;font-size: 14px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">对于</span><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.westca.com/House/articles/op=view_tag/tag=%BA%C0%D5%AC/lang=schinese.html?utm_source=westca&utm_medium=tag&utm_campaign=news_extend\" style=\";font-size: 14px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simhei, Georgia;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">豪宅</a><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simhei, Georgia;font-size: 14px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)