soft YaHei&#39;, 文泉驿正黑, &#39;WenQuanYi Zen Hei&#39;, 细明体, MingLiU;font-size: 14px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">中，178,120处房屋是有人住的，5,385处被豁免，2,538处空置。</span><br style=\"font-family: Verdana, sans-serif, 宋体, SimSun, 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 文泉驿正黑, &#39;WenQuanYi Zen Hei&#39;, 细明体, MingLiU;font-size: 14px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"/><br style=\"font-family: Verdana, sans-serif, 宋体, SimSun, 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 文泉驿正黑, &#39;WenQuanYi Zen Hei&#39;, 细明体, MingLiU;font-size: 14px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"/><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, sans-serif, 宋体, SimSun, 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 文泉驿正黑, &#39;WenQuanYi Zen Hei&#39;, 细明体, MingLiU;font-size: 14px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">温哥华市府预计今年空置税将总额超过3800万，包括已经收到的2100万。</span><br style=\"font-family: Verdana, sans-serif, 宋体, SimSun, 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 文泉驿正黑, &#39;WenQuanYi Zen Hei&#39;, 细明体, MingLiU;font-size: 14px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"/><br style=\"font-family: Verdana, sans-serif, 宋体, SimSun, 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 文泉驿正黑, &#39;WenQuanYi Zen Hei&#39;, 细明体, MingLiU;font-size: 14px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"/><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, sans-serif, 宋体, SimSun, 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 文泉驿正黑, &#39;WenQuanYi Zen Hei&#39;, 细明体, MingLiU;font-size: 14px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">这些钱将主要用来解决温哥华的住房危机，如修建保障性住房、廉</span><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.westca.com/News/tags/tag=%D7%E2%B7%BF/lang=schinese.html?utm_source=westca&utm_medium=tag&utm_campaign=news_extend\" style=\"background: none rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(0, 0, 153);font-size: 14px;font-family: Verdana, sans-serif, 宋体, SimSun, 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 文泉驿正黑, &#39;WenQuanYi Zen Hei&#39;, 细明体, MingLiU;white-space: normal\">租房</a><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, sans-serif, 宋体, SimSun, 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 文泉驿正黑, &#39;WenQuanYi Zen Hei&#39;, 细明体, MingLiU;font-size: 14px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">、廉价房、模板房等，此外还有改善</span><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.westca.com/News/tags/tag=%D7%B0%D0%DE/lang=schinese.html?utm_source=westca&utm_medium=tag&utm_campaign=news_extend\" style=\"background: none rgb(255, 255, 255);color: rgb(0, 0, 153);font-size: 14px;font-family: Verdana, sans-serif, 宋体, SimSun, 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 文泉驿正黑, &#39;WenQuanYi Zen Hei&#39;, 细明体, MingLiU;white-space: normal\">装修</a><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, sans-serif, 宋体, SimSun, 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 文泉驿正黑, &#39;WenQuanYi Zen Hei&#39;, 细明体, MingLiU;font-size: 14px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">、提供技能培训、帮助困难人士寻找房屋等。现已支出金额约800万。</span></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, sans-serif, 宋体, SimSun, 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 文泉驿正黑, &#39;WenQuanYi Zen Hei&#39;, 细明体, MingLiU;font-size: 14px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, sans-serif, 宋体, SimSun, 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 文泉驿正黑, &#39;WenQuanYi Zen Hei&#39;, 细明体, MingLiU;font-size: 14px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><br style=\"font-family: Verdana, sans-serif, 宋体, SimSun, 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 文泉驿正黑, &quot;WenQuanYi Zen Hei&quot;, 细明体, MingLiU; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20181219/1545181268690917.jpg\" title=\"1545181268690917.jpg\" alt=\"496f6f6f.jpg\"/><br style=\"font-family: Verdana, sans-serif, 宋体, SimSun, 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 文泉驿正黑, &quot;WenQuanYi Zen Hei&quot;, 细明体, MingLiU; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, sans-serif, 宋体, SimSun, 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 文泉驿正黑, &quot;WenQuanYi Zen Hei&quot;, 细明体, MingLiU; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">但空置税中也有很多种情况，可以获得空置税豁免权。如：</span><br style=\"font-family: Verdana, sans-serif, 宋体, SimSun, 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 文泉驿正黑, &quot;WenQuanYi Zen Hei&quot;, 细明体, MingLiU; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/><br style=\"font-family: Verdana, sans-serif, 宋体, SimSun, 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 文泉驿正黑, &quot;WenQuanYi Zen Hei&quot;, 细明体, MingLiU; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, sans-serif, 宋体, SimSun, 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 文泉驿正黑, &quot;WenQuanYi Zen Hei&quot;, 细明体, MingLiU; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">如果你的房屋被租住超过6个月以上，你将可以从空置税中豁免。</span><br style=\"font-family: Verdana, sans-serif, 宋体, SimSun, 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 文泉驿正黑, &quot;WenQuanYi Zen Hei&quot;, 细明体, MingLiU; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/><br style=\"font-family: Verdana, sans-serif, 宋体, SimSun, 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 文泉驿正黑, &quot;WenQuanYi Zen Hei&quot;, 细明体, MingLiU; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, sans-serif, 宋体, SimSun, 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 文泉驿正黑, &quot;WenQuanYi Zen Hei&quot;, 细明体, MingLiU; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">如果你的房屋空置期是正处于房屋上市待售时期，你也可以获得豁免。</span><br style=\"font-family: Verdana, sans-serif, 宋体, SimSun, 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 文泉驿正黑, &quot;WenQuanYi Zen Hei&quot;, 细明体, MingLiU; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/><br style=\"font-family: Verdana, sans-serif, 宋体, SimSun, 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 文泉驿正黑, &quot;WenQuanYi Zen Hei&quot;, 细明体, MingLiU; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, sans-serif, 宋体, SimSun, 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 文泉驿正黑, &quot;WenQuanYi Zen Hei&quot;, 细明体, MingLiU; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">