rmal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; line-height: 28.8px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; line-height: 28.8px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">https://vancouver.ca/home-property-development/declare-property-status.aspx</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; line-height: 28.8px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; line-height: 28.8px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">如果担心自己难以搞定一些复杂的问题，也可以咨询相关专业人士。</p><p><br/></p>',0,'2019-01-10 03:08:10','2019-01-10 10:01:06','房产信息','来帮大家研究一下豁免政策','/uploads/20190110/ba2928ad828771c929012782a3bfbb72.jpg','文章来源:加西周末 于2018年11月29日 新闻取自各大新闻媒体，新闻内容并不代表本网立场！'),(38,'卑诗出租法或将出现重大改变 ','<p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, 宋体; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">房主以房屋返修为理由，让租客搬离。租客们对这种潜在的“驱逐”充满了担忧。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, 宋体; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">为管理卑诗出租市场，卑诗省长贺谨（John Horgan）今年4月宣布成立出租房屋专责小组（Rental Housing Task Force），负责调查和检讨目前出租市场的问题。近日，专责小组已经完成调查，并向省府提交了包含23项建议的最终报告。如果这些建议的多数得以立法，那么卑诗出租市场将迎来大变革，尤其是对房东来说。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, 宋体; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">出租专责小组提23项建议</p><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, 宋体; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">明年或开始实施</p><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, 宋体; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">在进行深入的研究和调查后，出租房专责小组提出对《住宅租赁法》（Residential Tenancy Act）的修改建议报告。小组负责人温哥华西端选区（Vancouver-West End）省议员Spencer Herbert说，在和卑诗不同社区的不同居民交谈后，我们试图提出可以使出租法案更完善、对所有市民都公平的建议措施。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, 宋体; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">建议共有23项，包括停止驱逐租客、提高租房安全性、加大违规罚款、取消物业公司限制房东出租的权力、提高房屋供给和公平程序等。</p><p><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190110/1547061687381439.jpg\" title=\"1547061687381439.jpg\" alt=\"WeChat Image_20190109110333.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, 宋体; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">小组成员之一、温哥华岛萨尼治北与岛屿选区（Sannich North and the Islands）省议员Adam Olsen表示，我们仔细考虑了所有建议对房东及租客可能产生的影响，房客需要被保护，房东则需有权对自己的物业做出是否出租的决策。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, 宋体; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">小组的另一名成员，Courtenay-Comox选区省议员Ronna-Rae Leonard也指出，在卑诗省，无论是像温哥华或基隆那样的大城市，还是像盐泉岛一样的小地方，现有的出租制度都长期面临问题。“不同的地区情况不同，我们希望这些建议可以帮助完善。”</p><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, 宋体; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">在接下来的几个星期里，卑诗住房厅将开始审阅并讨论如何实施这些意见，也就是说，明年卑诗的住房法案很可能将会出现大变革。</p><p><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190110/1547061757793334.png\" title=\"1547061757793334.png\" alt=\"WeChat Screenshot_20190109112214.png\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, 宋体; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">在最终报告完成前，专项小组曾公布过几个参考意见，比如9月26日省府宣布将年加租幅度限制在通胀率2.5%，同时也设定了特殊条款，房东如果有重大翻修等情况，可以申增加高于限额的房租。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, 宋体; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">租客最担心遭房东驱逐</p><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, 宋体; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">新建议要求租客可居住在翻修房中</p><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, 宋体; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">报告中的第一项建议就是停止驱逐租客。专责小组表示，很多租客都表示，他们因为房东翻修房屋而遭到驱逐，即使他们已经明确表示翻修并不影响居住。一些租客认为，一旦房东发出了驱逐通知，他们就没办法再协商，而且也无法确认房东说的装修是真是假，租客们对这种潜在的“驱逐”充满了担忧。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, 宋体; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">专责小组认为，省府需要为此明确立法。如果租客同意在装修条件下居住，除非有证据表明租客无法正常居住，否则装修期间租客也可居住；只有在很少的情况下，租客才能被要求离开，比如重大和长期的房屋装修会对租客造成健康和安全风险。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, 宋体; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">如果新法实行，那么如换窗户、水管及电线系统等装修，都不再能成为驱逐租客的理由。而且装修完成后，房东需要首先询问暂时离开的租客是否愿意以同样或相似的租金继续回来居住。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, 宋体; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">温哥华市议会近日也通过了一项类似的规定，“租户搬迁及保障条例”（Tenant Relocation and Protection Policy）修改动议。根据动议，那些因为屋主重新装修或房屋重建而迁出的租户，在工程完成后，可以以同样的租金搬回来继续租住同样的单位。而且，屋主不能因为这个借口而让人搬家，或将租金调高。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, 宋体; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">提出动议的COPE市议员Jean Swanson表示，这样不但能保障租客，还能避免温哥华的租金不断攀升。</p><p><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190110/1547061806342926.png\" title=\"1547061806342926.png\" alt=\"WeChat Screenshot_20190109112310.png\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, 宋体; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">虽然很多市民都对此支持，但一些房东则认为不合理。BC业主协会（LandlordBC）的CEO David Hutniak说：“这样的政策，会使得那些原本打算翻新房屋的老旧房屋屋主冻结原来的计划，不再进行房屋的维护。”据悉，温哥华有超过一半出租单位，房龄为50至70年，老化的建筑必然会出现维护问题。有提议称，省府和市府的限制驱逐政策应该有更详细的说明，考虑到可能会出现的其他情况。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, 宋体; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">新报告中的其他主要建议还包括：在拆除专用租赁房的情况下，与当地政府合作制定租户补偿和搬迁指南计划，保障租客利益；通过取消物业公司禁止业主分租的权力，增加可负担住房；与当地政府合作制定、实施和执行严格的短期租赁规范，以更好地保护长期租赁存量。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, 宋体; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">女租客告房东案备受关注</p><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, 宋体; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">判决结果或成先例</p><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, 宋体; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">之前一个女租客因被驱赶而上诉法院的案例也备受关注，业内人士认为，因为这是卑诗省相关出租问题的首个案例，此案结果会影响以后的判决。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, 宋体; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">温哥华女房客Vivian Baumann在温西的一栋公寓大楼住了17年，2014年该大楼被投资公司AARTI Investments Ltd.购下。新房东接手公寓后表示，愿意向所有租户提供4个月租金等额的款项，以换取租户搬离大楼；不愿搬离的租户则被要求同意“大幅”增加租金。Baumann表示，新房东提出的租金1200元在她当时租金730元基础上增幅64%，远超过法律允许加租范围，因此她拒绝接受加租，也拒绝搬离大楼。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, 宋体; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">随后Baumann收到新房东以翻修住房为名发出的驱逐令，Baumann曾提出在翻修后仍回来居住，但不被允许。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, 宋体; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Baumann经了解后得知，房东当时未持有翻修工作所需的许可证，她与技术人员交谈后还发现，房东所称的翻修工作无需清空住宅便可实现。Baumann向住宅租赁部门（Residential Tenancy Branch，RTB）提出投诉，声称要其搬迁是房东希望加租，而不是对她的单位进行翻修。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, 宋体; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">不过，省府租务处仲裁人驳回了Vivian Baumann的案件，随后Baumann收到两天时间必须搬出的通知。此后Baumann又上诉到卑诗最高法院，诉讼获胜，但她的房东又提出上诉。在等待法院最后判决的同时，这个案子已经引起了高度关注。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, 宋体; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">在2018年中大温公寓出租报告中就提到，尽管这个案子结果未知，但这种潜在的法律改变会影响未来大温的房屋出租。加上现在温市府和省府都已经关注了驱逐房客的事情，未来不排除有更严格的规定出台。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, 宋体; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">其实近两年卑诗省府已经推出多项出租管制措施，如堵塞定期合同中的漏洞，废除地理加租条款；加强对租客的保护，避免他们因房屋翻修或重建而遭受重大损失；规范非法短期租赁，提高物业罚款数额等。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, 宋体; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">专责小组的调查报告显示，租客认为市场上最大的挑战就是出租房源不充足，大温居民还是迫切希望省府能够在规范出租市场的同时增加市场供应。研究公司Mario Canseco的新调查也有同样的结果，约三分之一大温居民（34％）希望未来几年内建造更多的租赁单位。</p><p><br/></p>',0,'2019-01-10 03:30:10','2019-01-10 09:57:43','房产信息','房屋翻修租客仍可居住其中','/uploads/20190110/bca71b961bc04e9c22f53bdf06a4a9a3.jpg','文章来源:加西周末 于2018年12月23日 新闻取自各大新闻媒体，新闻内容并不代表本网立场！'),(39,'BC估价局陆续向业主寄出物业估价单 ','<p>BC估价局这个星期开始向业主寄出物业估价单, 公众同时可以登上估价局的网站查寻<span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, 宋体; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">物业的估价。根据上年首五个最有价值的房地产估价中, 今年全部平均下跌七个百分点。</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, 宋体; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190110/1547062579158081.jpg\" title=\"1547062579158081.jpg\" alt=\"PropertyTax_jpg_800x1000_q100-1.jpg\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, 宋体; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, 宋体; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">BC大学城市经济与房地产中心的高级研究员Tsur Sommerville指, 物业估价跟随市场变动, 2019年矮层公寓及排屋的估价可能会大幅上升, 而独立屋的估价就可能不变甚至下降,有机会导致低陆平原矮层公寓和排屋的基准物业税调升。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, 宋体; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">而物业估价师Paul Sullivan就说, 因为省府向有较高价值的房屋征收额外税项, 例如向市值高于300万的物业征收学校税, 令到它们的销售数字和估价都下跌。他预计, 温哥华高尚住宅的估值下调会令受影响的房屋净价一+共下跌超过一百亿元。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, 宋体; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></span><br/></p>',0,'2019-01-10 03:36:39','2019-01-10 09:58:34','房产信息','BC估价局这个星期开始向业主寄出物业估价单, 公众同时可以登上估价局的网站查寻','/uploads/20190110/19e3ff5c3584f76c5ea789a03e947882.jpg','文章来源:加拿大中文电台 于2019年1月2日 新闻取自各大新闻媒体，新闻内容并不代表本网立场！'),(40,'大温新屋开工量新低 独立屋缩减最多','<p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simhei, Georgia;font-size: 14px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">1月9日，加拿大抵押贷款与</span><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.westca.com/House/articles/op=view_tag/tag=%B7%BF%CE%DD/lang=schinese.html?utm_source=westca&utm_medium=tag&utm_campaign=news_extend\" style=\";font-size: 14px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simhei, Georgia;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">房屋</a><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simhei, Georgia;font-size: 14px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">公司</span><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.westca.com/House/articles/op=view_tag/tag=CMHC/lang=schinese.html?utm_source=westca&utm_medium=tag&utm_campaign=news_extend\" style=\";font-size: 14px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simhei, Georgia;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">CMHC</a><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simhei, Georgia;font-size: 14px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">发布全国</span><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.westca.com/House/articles/op=view_tag/tag=%D0%C2%CE%DD%B6%AF%B9%A4/lang=schinese.html?utm_source=westca&utm_medium=tag&utm_campaign=news_extend\" style=\";font-size: 14px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simhei, Georgia;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">新屋动工</a><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simhei, Georgia;font-size: 14px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">数量报告显示，加拿大新屋动工量创新低，</span><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.westca.com/House/articles/op=view_tag/tag=%B4%F3%CE%C2/lang=schinese.html?utm_source=westca&utm_medium=tag&utm_campaign=news_extend\" style=\";font-size: 14px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simhei, Georgia;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">大温</a><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simhei, Georgia;font-size: 14px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">最低的地区倒是很出乎意料。</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simhei, Georgia;font-size: 14px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190110/1547062903878967.jpg\" title=\"1547062903878967.jpg\" alt=\"664f6c53.jpg\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simhei, Georgia;font-size: 14px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simhei, Georgia;font-size: 14px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">BC省来看，</span><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.westca.com/House/articles/op=view_tag/tag=%B6%C0%C1%A2%CE%DD/lang=schinese.html?utm_source=westca&utm_medium=tag&utm_campaign=news_extend\" style=\";font-size: 14px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simhei, Georgia;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">独立屋</a><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simhei, Georgia;font-size: 14px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">2018年12月数据缩减14%，但其他户型则小幅涨1%。</span><br style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simhei, Georgia;font-size: 14px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"/><br style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simhei, Georgia;font-size: 14px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"/><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simhei, Georgia;font-size: 14px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">对比全国形势基本一致。</span><br style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simhei, Georgia;font-size: 14px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"/><br style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simhei, Georgia;font-size: 14px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"/><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simhei, Georgia;font-size: 14px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">独立屋新开工数量12月缩减21%，其他户型增长9%。</span></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simhei, Georgia;font-size: 14px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190110/1547062941926452.jpg\" title=\"1547062941926452.jpg\" alt=\"58552b4c (1).jpg\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simhei, Georgia;font-size: 14px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simhei, Georgia;font-size: 14px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">从2018年全年来看，BC省新屋动工数量减少7%，其中独立屋减少11%，联排和</span><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.westca.com/House/articles/op=view_tag/tag=%B9%AB%D4%A2/lang=schinese.html?utm_source=westca&utm_medium=tag&utm_campaign=news_extend\" style=\";font-size: 14px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simhei, Georgia;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">公寓</a><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simhei, Georgia;font-size: 14px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">减少5%。</span></span></p><p><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190110/1547062977267211.jpg\" title=\"1547062977267211.jpg\" alt=\"76693441.jpg\"/></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simhei, Georgia;font-size: 14px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">大温地区2018年12月新屋动工数量继续走低，全年来看，</span><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.westca.com/House/articles/op=view_tag/tag=%CE%C2%B8%E7%BB%AA/lang=schinese.html?utm_source=westca&utm_medium=tag&utm_campaign=news_extend\" style=\";font-size: 14px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simhei, Georgia;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">温哥华</a><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simhei, Georgia;font-size: 14px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">的新屋动工量比2017年减少11%。</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simhei, Georgia;font-size: 14px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simhei, Georgia;font-size: 14px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">而</span><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.westca.com/House/articles/op=view_tag/tag=%D0%C2%CE%DD%B6%AF%B9%A4/lang=schinese.html?utm_source=westca&utm_medium=tag&utm_campaign=news_extend\" style=\";font-size: 14px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simhei, Georgia;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">新屋动工</a><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simhei, Georgia;font-size: 14px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">数量降幅最大的竟是</span><strong style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simhei, Georgia;font-size: 14px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.westca.com/House/articles/op=view_tag/tag=%CB%D8%C0%EF/lang=schinese.html?utm_source=westca&utm_medium=tag&utm_campaign=news_extend\" style=\";color: rgb(51, 51, 51)\">素里</a></strong><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simhei, Georgia;font-size: 14px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">，2018年比2017年减少27%。而根据加拿大人口普查统计显示，素里市是近年来BC省人口增长最快的城市。</span></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simhei, Georgia;font-size: 14px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190110/1547063040465576.jpg\" title=\"1547063040465576.jpg\" alt=\"645a316e.jpg\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simhei, Georgia;font-size: 14px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simhei, Georgia;font-size: 14px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">这些降幅都将使两市的租</span><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.westca.com/House/articles/op=view_tag/tag=%B7%BF%CA%D0/lang=schinese.html?utm_source=westca&utm_medium=tag&utm_campaign=news_extend\" style=\";font-size: 14px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simhei, Georgia;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">房市</a><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simhei, Georgia;font-size: 14px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">场更加紧俏。</span><br style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simhei, Georgia;font-size: 14px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"/><br style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simhei, Georgia;font-size: 14px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"/><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simhei, Georgia;font-size: 14px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">此外，BC省首府</span><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.westca.com/House/articles/op=view_tag/tag=%CE%AC%B6%E0%C0%FB%D1%C7/lang=schinese.html?utm_source=westca&utm_medium=tag&utm_campaign=news_extend\" style=\";font-size: 14px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simhei, Georgia;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">维多利亚</a><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simhei, Georgia;font-size: 14px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">大区的新屋动工数量12月创造了自1976年以来的历史新低。</span><br style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simhei, Georgia;font-size: 14px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"/><br style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simhei, Georgia;font-size: 14px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"/><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simhei, Georgia;font-size: 14px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">由于</span><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.westca.com/House/articles/op=view_tag/tag=%D7%E2%B7%BF/lang=schinese.html?utm_source=westca&utm_medium=tag&utm_campaign=news_extend\" style=\";font-size: 14px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simhei, Georgia;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">租房</a><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simhei, Georgia;font-size: 14px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">需求增加和空置率低，2018年维多利亚地区的新开工</span><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.westca.com/House/articles/op=view_tag/tag=%B7%BF%CE%DD/lang=schinese.html?utm_source=westca&utm_medium=tag&utm_campaign=news_extend\" style=\";font-size: 14px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simhei, Georgia;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">房屋</a><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simhei, Georgia;font-size: 14px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">建设中，至少一半属租赁房屋。</span></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simhei, Georgia;font-size: 14px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simhei, Georgia;font-size: 14px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><br style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simhei, Georgia;font-size: 14px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"/><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.westca.com/House/articles/op=view_tag/tag=CMHC/lang=schinese.html?utm_source=westca&utm_medium=tag&utm_campaign=news_extend\" style=\";font-size: 14px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simhei, Georgia;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">CMHC</a><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simhei, Georgia;font-size: 14px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">统计显示，从加拿大全国来看，2018年整体开工数量少于2017年，主要减少来自于</span><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.westca.com/House/articles/op=view_tag/tag=%B6%C0%C1%A2%CE%DD/lang=schinese.html?utm_source=westca&utm_medium=tag&utm_campaign=news_extend\" style=\";font-size: 14px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simhei, Georgia;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">独立屋</a><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simhei, Georgia;font-size: 14px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">的减少，而联排城市屋和</span><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.westca.com/House/articles/op=view_tag/tag=%B9%AB%D4%A2/lang=schinese.html?utm_source=westca&utm_medium=tag&utm_campaign=news_extend\" style=\";font-size: 14px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simhei, Georgia;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">公寓</a><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, simhei, Georgia;font-size: 14px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">建设则数量小幅增长。总体而言，虽然，新屋动工数量连跌5个月，但仍然高于历史平均水平。</span></span></p>',0,'2019-01-10 03:44:48','2019-01-10 09:59:22','房产信息','全国新屋动工数量报告显示，加拿大新屋动工量创新低','/uploads/20190110/9980b651ef24210c4c8a7489b88517e0.jpg','文章来源:加西网 于2019年1月9日 新闻取自各大新闻媒体，新闻内容并不代表本网立场！'),(41,'天铁开工，房价上涨， 这个社区却叫停新房建设','<p><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190111/1547144225936828.jpg\" title=\"1547144225936828.jpg\" alt=\"1.jpg\"/></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: DengXian;background: white\">该社区居民协会主席</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;background: white\">Mike Bola</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: DengXian;background: white\">对媒体表示，在公共基础设施不到位之前，他们的社区已经够拥挤了，不欢迎更多的住宅！</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: Verdana, sans-serif\"><br/> <img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190111/1547144300349914.jpg\" title=\"1547144300349914.jpg\" alt=\"2.jpg\"/><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190111/1547144304321441.jpg\" title=\"1547144304321441.jpg\" alt=\"3.jpg\"/> </span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: Verdana, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: DengXian;background: white\">而竞选时承诺将要给这个社区新添冰球场馆和图书馆的市长</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;background: white\">Doug McCallum</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: DengXian;background: white\">在上任后，</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;background: white\">“</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: DengXian;background: white\">惊讶的发现</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;background: white\">”</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: DengXian;background: white\">市政府欠债太多，因此把之前承诺的诸多项目一并叫停，其中就包括</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;background: white\">Cloverdale</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: DengXian;background: white\">社区的这些基础设施项目。</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: Verdana, sans-serif\"><br/> <img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190111/1547144369195892.jpg\" title=\"1547144369195892.jpg\" alt=\"4.jpg\"/><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190111/1547144378869750.jpg\" title=\"1547144378869750.jpg\" alt=\"5.jpg\"/> </span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: Verdana, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: Verdana, sans-serif\"></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;background: white\">Cloverdale</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: DengXian;background: white\">和</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;background: white\">Cloverdale Heights</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: DengXian;background: white\">早已是非常成熟的社区，这几年城市联排屋和</span><a href=\"http://www.westca.com/News/tags/tag=%B9%AB%D4%A2/lang=schinese.html?utm_source=westca&utm_medium=tag&utm_campaign=news_extend\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:107%;font-family:DengXian;color:#000099;background:white\">公寓</span></a><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: DengXian;background: white\">的快速发展，使得这片社区人口激增</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif;background: white\">。</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;background: white\">Mike Bola</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: DengXian;background: white\">表示，社区人口暴涨，大部分新增的都是以家庭为单位的人口，那些家庭带来的孩子已经非常多了，超过了这个社区原本能够承受的负荷</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif;background: white\">。</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: DengXian;background: white\">孩子们现在根本没地方去玩！</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: Verdana, sans-serif\"><br/> <br/> </span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: DengXian;background: white\">此外，也有其他人士担心，这个社区里由于新屋建设太多、人口增长太快，使得学校也变得拥挤不堪。交通也变得更加拥堵。市民的生活质量也随之大打折扣。</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: Verdana, sans-serif\"><br/> <img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190111/1547144456830383.jpg\" title=\"1547144456830383.jpg\" alt=\"6.jpg\"/> </span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: Verdana, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: Verdana, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;background: white\">Mike Bola</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: DengXian;background: white\">表示，社区代表们认为，什么时候</span><span style=\"font-size:15px;line-height:107%;font-family:&#39;Calibri&#39;,sans-serif\"><a href=\"http://www.westca.com/News/tags/tag=%CB%D8%C0%EF/lang=schinese.html?utm_source=westca&utm_medium=tag&utm_campaign=news_extend\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:107%;font-family:DengXian;color:#000099;background:white\">素里</span></a></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: DengXian;background: white\">市长打算重启公共设施项目之后，再考虑在这里开发建新房！</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: Verdana, sans-serif\"><br/> <br/> </span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: DengXian;background: white\">此前，素里市在举行市政预算听证会时，宣布撤销掉原有公共基础设施建设计划，很多社区居民和孩子们就很失望离开。</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: Verdana, sans-serif\"><br/> <br/> </span><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190111/1547144480481506.jpg\" title=\"1547144480481506.jpg\" alt=\"7.jpg\"/></span></span><br/></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: Verdana, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: Verdana, sans-serif\"></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:107%;font-family:DengXian;color:black;background:white\">会议开始前，一些来自</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:107%;font-family:&#39;Verdana&#39;,sans-serif;color:black;background:white\">Cloverdale</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:107%;font-family:DengXian;color:black;background:white\">的青少年和家长们聚集在市政厅门口，但市长</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:107%;font-family:&#39;Verdana&#39;,sans-serif;color:black;background:white\">Doug McCallum</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:107%;font-family:DengXian;color:black;background:white\">告诉孩子们，抗议牌将不能带进会场</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:107%;font-family:&#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;,sans-serif;color:black;background:white\">。</span></p><p><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190111/1547144525860717.jpg\" title=\"1547144525860717.jpg\" alt=\"8.jpg\"/><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: Verdana, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: Verdana, sans-serif\"></span></span><br/></p><p><span style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:107%;font-family:DengXian;color:black;background:white\">面对各种质疑声，</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:107%;font-family:&#39;Verdana&#39;,sans-serif;color:black;background:white\">Doug McCallum</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:107%;font-family:DengXian;color:black;background:white\">表示，素里面临巨大的债务，要按照适合素里的方式来决定市政安排</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:107%;font-family:&#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;,sans-serif;color:black;background:white\">。</span></p><p><br/></p>',0,'2019-01-11 02:23:07','2019-01-11 02:23:07','房产信息','在Cloverdale大温的房产开发正火热，但却被这里的居民集体叫停了！为什么？','/uploads/20190111/8006b17d3b4321112c9ee63d4d5551b2.jpg','文章来源:加西网 于2019年1月8日 新闻取自各大新闻媒体，新闻内容并不代表本网立场！'),(42,'列治文短租房出新规 华人房主请注意','<p><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190111/1547145265201354.jpg\" title=\"1547145265201354.jpg\" alt=\"01.jpg\"/></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: DengXian;background: white\">据列治文市发言人</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;background: white\">Ted Townsend</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: DengXian;background: white\">介绍，现有列治文市对违规的短</span><span style=\"font-size:15px;line-height:107%;font-family:&#39;Calibri&#39;,sans-serif\"><a href=\"http://www.westca.com/News/tags/tag=%D7%E2%B7%BF/lang=schinese.html?utm_source=westca&utm_medium=tag&utm_campaign=news_extend\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:107%;font-family:DengXian;color:#000099;background:white\">租房</span></a></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: DengXian;background: white\">采取最高罚款</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;background: white\">1000</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: DengXian;background: white\">元的措施。但每次争议都由</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;background: white\">BC</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: DengXian;background: white\">省法院来处理，可能会需要很长时间。</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: Verdana, sans-serif\"><br/> <br/> </span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: DengXian;background: white\">为此，列治文市计划引入第二个惩罚措施选项，将交付更少的罚金、并且缩短裁决解决的时间。</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: Verdana, sans-serif\"><br/> <img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190111/1547145290900329.jpg\" title=\"1547145290900329.jpg\" alt=\"02.jpg\"/> </span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: Verdana, sans-serif\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190111/1547145385457580.jpg\" title=\"1547145385457580.jpg\" alt=\"03.jpg\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: Verdana, sans-serif\"></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;background: white\">Ted Townsend</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: DengXian;background: white\">表示，根据新规，对于出现违规的业主，市政府将每次处以最高</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;background: white\">500</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: DengXian;background: white\">元的罚金。在争议解决的流程方面，无需经过省级法院来裁决，而由市级法院裁决，可以减少处理时间以及相关的法律诉讼费用。</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: Verdana, sans-serif\"><br/> <br/> </span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: DengXian;background: white\">该议案提出得到了列治文市议会的普遍支持</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif;background: white\">。</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: DengXian;background: white\">毕竟，政府的目的是为了惩戒和</span><span style=\"font-size:15px;line-height:107%;font-family:&#39;Calibri&#39;,sans-serif\"><a href=\"http://www.westca.com/News/tags/tag=%BD%CC%D3%FD/lang=schinese.html?utm_source=westca&utm_medium=tag&utm_campaign=news_extend\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:107%;font-family:DengXian;color:#000099;background:white\">教育</span></a></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: DengXian;background: white\">短租房业主，使市场更加规范化，而不是为了收更多的罚金。</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: Verdana, sans-serif\"><br/> <img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190111/1547145445968841.jpg\" title=\"1547145445968841.jpg\" alt=\"04.jpg\"/> </span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: Verdana, sans-serif\"></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: DengXian;background: white\">据报道，去年，列治文市发放了</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;background: white\">75</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: DengXian;background: white\">张非法短期罚单，并收取了</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;background: white\">36,000</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: DengXian;background: white\">元的罚款。</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;background: white\">2017</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: DengXian;background: white\">年，发出</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;background: white\">87</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: DengXian;background: white\">张罚单，收入</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;background: white\">41,800</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: DengXian;background: white\">元。</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: Verdana, sans-serif\"><br/> <br/> </span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: DengXian;background: white\">列治文现有合法短租房</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;background: white\">610</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: DengXian;background: white\">个</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif;background: white\">。</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: DengXian;background: white\">自</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;background: white\">2017</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: DengXian;background: white\">年以来，该市已经裁定了</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;background: white\">541</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: DengXian;background: white\">个非法租赁</span><span style=\"font-size:15px;line-height: 107%;font-family:&#39;Calibri&#39;,sans-serif\"><a href=\"http://www.westca.com/News/tags/tag=%B7%BF%CE%DD/lang=schinese.html?utm_source=westca&utm_medium=tag&utm_campaign=news_extend\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:107%;font-family:DengXian;color:#000099;background:white\">房屋</span></a></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: DengXian;background: white\">，其中</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;background: white\">524</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: DengXian;background: white\">个已被停止运营。</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: Verdana, sans-serif\"><br/> <br/> </span><span style=\"font-size:15px;line-height:107%;font-family:&#39;Calibri&#39;,sans-serif\"><a href=\"http://www.westca.com/News/tags/tag=%C1%D0%D6%CE%CE%C4/lang=schinese.html?utm_source=westca&utm_medium=tag&utm_campaign=news_extend\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:107%;font-family:DengXian;color:#000099;background:white\">列治文</span></a></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: DengXian;background: white\">市一度是</span><span style=\"font-size:15px;line-height: 107%;font-family:&#39;Calibri&#39;,sans-serif\"><a href=\"http://www.westca.com/News/tags/tag=%B4%F3%CE%C2/lang=schinese.html?utm_source=westca&utm_medium=tag&utm_campaign=news_extend\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:107%;font-family:DengXian;color:#000099;background:white\">大温</span></a></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: DengXian;background: white\">地区短</span><span style=\"font-size:15px;line-height: 107%;font-family:&#39;Calibri&#39;,sans-serif\"><a href=\"http://www.westca.com/News/tags/tag=%D7%E2%B7%BF/lang=schinese.html?utm_source=westca&utm_medium=tag&utm_campaign=news_extend\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:107%;font-family:DengXian;color:#000099;background:white\">租房</span></a></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: DengXian;background: white\">最繁华的地段，离机场近的天然优势、华人多的语言文化优势等造就了这一局面。</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: Verdana, sans-serif\"><br/> <img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190111/1547145491912384.jpg\" title=\"1547145491912384.jpg\" alt=\"05.jpg\"/> </span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: Verdana, sans-serif\"></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:107%;font-family:DengXian;color:black;background:white\">但短租房也引发很多交通、噪音污染等问题，为此，</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:107%;font-family:&#39;Verdana&#39;,sans-serif;color:black;background:white\">2017</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height:107%;font-family:DengXian;color:black;background:white\">年</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:107%;font-family:&#39;Verdana&#39;,sans-serif;color:black;background:white\">4</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:107%;font-family:DengXian;color:black;background:white\">月</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;line-height: 107%;font-family:&#39;Verdana&#39;,sans-serif;color:black;background:white\">30</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:107%;font-family:DengXian;color:black;background:white\">日，列治文市通过决议，除了那些已经申请了</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:107%;font-family:&#39;Verdana&#39;,sans-serif;color:black;background:white\">AirBnb</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height:107%;font-family:DengXian;color:black;background:white\">牌照的业主外，私人短租行为将被视为违法。</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:107%;font-family:&#39;Verdana&#39;,sans-serif;color:black\"><br/> <br/> </span><span style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:107%;font-family: DengXian;color:black;background:white\">包括业主</span><a href=\"http://www.westca.com/News/tags/tag=%B3%F6%D7%E2/lang=schinese.html?utm_source=westca&utm_medium=tag&utm_campaign=news_extend\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:107%;font-family:DengXian;color:#000099;background:white\">出租</span></a><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height:107%;font-family:DengXian;color:black;background:white\">整栋物业、也禁止套间、</span><a href=\"http://www.westca.com/News/tags/tag=%BA%F3%CF%EF%CE%DD/lang=schinese.html?utm_source=westca&utm_medium=tag&utm_campaign=news_extend\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:107%;font-family:DengXian;color:#000099;background:white\">后巷屋</span></a><span style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:107%;font-family:DengXian;color:black;background:white\">以及附加屋的短租房形式，出租时间在</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:107%;font-family:&#39;Verdana&#39;,sans-serif;color:black;background:white\">30</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:107%;font-family:DengXian;color:black;background:white\">天及</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:107%;font-family:&#39;Verdana&#39;,sans-serif;color:black;background:white\">30</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:107%;font-family:DengXian;color:black;background:white\">天以内</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:107%;font-family:&#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;,sans-serif;color:black;background:white\">。</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:0;margin-bottom:0;line-height: normal\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;,sans-serif;color:black;background:white\">并规定每间房最多只可出租给两个人。</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;Verdana&#39;,sans-serif;color:black\"><br/> <br/> </span><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;,sans-serif;color:black;background:white\">违例者将面临高额罚款，罚金高达每天</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;Verdana&#39;,sans-serif;color:black;background:white\">$1,000</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;,sans-serif;color:black;background:white\">元。</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: Verdana, sans-serif\"><br/></span><br/></p>',0,'2019-01-11 02:38:32','2019-01-11 02:38:32','房产信息','列治文市政府表示，对短租房违规者将引入新的惩罚措施选项。','/uploads/20190111/a34f7b0f81b685a2239f53cadf1f7f02.jpg','文章来源:加西网 于2019年1月7日 新闻取自各大新闻媒体，新闻内容并不代表本网立场！'),(43,'素里天车即将开工！计划书大曝光 这些地方将设8个天车站','<p style=\"margin-bottom:16px;line-height:normal;background: #FAFAFC\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:&#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;,sans-serif;color:#444444\">根据</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:&#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;,sans-serif;color:#444444\">Translink的初步计划书，全程长16公里的素里至兰里天车线的兴建，预计在2025年完成，有关计划书将在周四的市长议会( Mayor’s Council)上提出。</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:16px;line-height:normal;background: #FAFAFC\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:&#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;,sans-serif;color:#444444\">Translink的计划书还没有提供沿菲沙公路(Fraser Hwy)兴建天车线的造价，但透露仅2019年进行的“设计前”(pre-design)阶段，就需要动用3000万元。</span></p><p><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190111/1547146460315765.jpg\" title=\"1547146460315765.jpg\" alt=\"001.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:16px;line-height:normal;background: #FAFAFC\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:&#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;,sans-serif;color:#444444\">预计天车项目总成本没有更新数据，还是之前预计的</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:&#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;,sans-serif;color:#444444\">29亿元，其中包括7.3亿元（25％）的应急费用。</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:16px;line-height:normal;background: #FAFAFC\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:&#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;,sans-serif;color:#444444\">根据计划书，该条</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:&#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;,sans-serif;color:#444444\">16公里长的天车线，将设有8个站，及预留第9个站将来扩充时兴建，为了运行这条线路，Translink需增加额外55辆天车。</span></p><p><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190111/1547146474944000.jpg\" title=\"1547146474944000.jpg\" alt=\"002.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:16px;line-height:normal;background: #FAFAFC\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:&#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;,sans-serif;color:#444444\">公共交通管理部门制定了一个潜在的</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:&#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;,sans-serif;color:#444444\">15个月的时间表来制定初步计划和商业案例，以便在2020年中期之前向私人承包商发放资格申请。之后，采购还需要15个月，真正的施工周期大约需要四年时间。</span></p><p><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190111/1547146513550537.jpg\" title=\"1547146513550537.jpg\" alt=\"003.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:16px;line-height:normal;background: #FAFAFC\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:&#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;,sans-serif;color:#444444\">假如市长议会通过有关计划书，</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:&#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;,sans-serif;color:#444444\">Translink董事会也会支持方案。之后，Translink就会开始进入下一期工作，包括订立工作流程计划、职员及顾问工作、与素里及兰里市府详细规划B-Line公交线的处理，并将于明年1月向市长议会报告进展。</span></p><p><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190111/1547146555273193.jpg\" title=\"1547146555273193.jpg\" alt=\"004.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:16px;line-height:normal;background: #FAFAFC\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:&#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;,sans-serif;color:#444444\">现任素里市长麦卡勒姆</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:&#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;,sans-serif;color:#444444\">(Doug McCallum)在10月市选竞选时，提出推翻三级政府资金已到位的轻轨计划，并改为兴建连接现有天车系统的素里-兰里列车线，当时他表示超过八成素里市民反对素里轻轨。素里轻轨计划已获得联邦及省府承诺拨款16.5亿元，Translink到目前为止花在素里轻轨的直接规划、环境评估及商业计划的成本已达到5000万元，素里市也已花费了2000万元。麦卡勒姆坚持，天车计划所需的经费，与轻轨差不多。</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:16px;line-height:normal;background: #FAFAFC\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:&#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;,sans-serif;color:#444444\">与之前素里市长所鼓吹的：用现有</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:&#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;,sans-serif;color:#444444\">LRT资金16亿元、4年时间建好天车差的是多了点……但总是有了点盼头……</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:16px;line-height:normal;background: #FAFAFC\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:&#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;,sans-serif;color:#444444\">Translink预估，天车建成后，从素里到兰里全程需要约22分钟，这比当时提出的LRT轻轨要快13分钟还多。</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:16px;line-height:normal;background: #FAFAFC\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:&#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;,sans-serif;color:#444444\">好事成双，百老汇的天车延长线也已经被提上了日程，</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:&#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;,sans-serif;color:#444444\">2025年大温将会收获两条新的天车线。</span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:16px;line-height:normal;background: #FAFAFC\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:&#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;,sans-serif;color:#444444\">而且</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:&#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;,sans-serif;color:#444444\">Translink还考虑给新建的天车站建厕所！12月8日，Translink董事会批准了员工的建议，将在未来的天车站内建厕所，提高用户体验，保证安全。</span></p><p><br/></p>',0,'2019-01-11 02:56:18','2019-01-11 02:56:18','社区规划','','/uploads/20190111/3d1bbb5d29671d0949f03bd95ecaa12e.jpg','文章来源:爱素里 于2018年12月12日 新闻取自各大新闻媒体，新闻内容并不代表本网立场！'),(44,'加国经济形势预测大变样 央行暂不加息','<p><span style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:107%;font-family:DengXian;color:black;background:white\">加拿大央行</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:107%;font-family:&#39;Verdana&#39;,sans-serif;color:black;background:white\">1</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:107%;font-family:DengXian;color:black;background:white\">月</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:107%;font-family:&#39;Verdana&#39;,sans-serif;color:black;background:white\">9</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:107%;font-family:DengXian;color:black;background:white\">日早晨发布新闻称，将维持隔夜</span><a href=\"http://www.westca.com/News/tags/tag=%C0%FB%C2%CA/lang=schinese.html?utm_source=westca&utm_medium=tag&utm_campaign=news_extend\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:107%;font-family:DengXian;color:#000099;background:white\">利率</span></a><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height:107%;font-family:DengXian;color:black;background:white\">在</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:107%;font-family:&#39;Verdana&#39;,sans-serif;color:black;background:white\">1.75%</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height:107%;font-family:DengXian;color:black;background:white\">。银行利率在</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:107%;font-family:&#39;Verdana&#39;,sans-serif;color:black;background:white\">2%</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:107%;font-family:DengXian;color:black;background:white\">，存款利率在</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:107%;font-family:&#39;Verdana&#39;,sans-serif;color:black;background:white\">1.5%</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:107%;font-family:DengXian;color:black;background:white\">。今天早晨央行也同时发布了最新的货币政策分析报告。报告口风与</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:107%;font-family:&#39;Verdana&#39;,sans-serif;color:black;background:white\">10</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:107%;font-family:DengXian;color:black;background:white\">月大不同</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height:107%;font-family:&#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;,sans-serif;color:black;background:white\">。</span></p><p><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190111/1547148099409393.jpg\" title=\"1547148099409393.jpg\" alt=\"0001.jpg\"/><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190111/1547148103717163.jpg\" title=\"1547148103717163.jpg\" alt=\"0002.jpg\"/></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: DengXian;background: white\">这与上周的一些机构预测一致。</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: Verdana, sans-serif\"><br/> <br/> </span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: DengXian;background: white\">虽然央行表示暂停加息，却没有对加元走势造成影响，加元兑美元今天继续上扬。</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: Verdana, sans-serif\"><br/> <br/> </span><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190111/1547148182469635.jpg\" title=\"1547148182469635.jpg\" alt=\"0003.jpg\"/></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: DengXian;background: white\">截止至发稿时为止，加元与美元的汇率为</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;background: white\">1</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: DengXian;background: white\">加元兑</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;background: white\">75.66</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: DengXian;background: white\">美分，较昨日上涨了</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;background: white\">0.42%</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: DengXian;background: white\">。</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: Verdana, sans-serif\"><br/> <br/> </span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: DengXian;background: white\">加元兑美元自</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;background: white\">1</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: DengXian;background: white\">月</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;background: white\">2</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: DengXian;background: white\">日以来就一直上扬，据路透社的调查显示，加元预计将在</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;background: white\">2019</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: DengXian;background: white\">年反弹，恢复去年的部分跌幅。</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: Verdana, sans-serif\"><br/> <br/> </span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: DengXian;background: white\">对超过</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;background: white\">50</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: DengXian;background: white\">位货币分析师的调查显示，加元与美元的汇率预计在</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;background: white\">12</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: DengXian;background: white\">个月内将升至</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;background: white\">1.28</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: DengXian;background: white\">加元对</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;background: white\">1</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: DengXian;background: white\">美元，或者</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;background: white\">1</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: DengXian;background: white\">加元兑</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;background: white\">78.13</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: DengXian;background: white\">美分。</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: Verdana, sans-serif\"><br/> <br/> </span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: DengXian;background: white\">加拿大统计局昨天发布的贸易统计数据显示，去年</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;background: white\">11</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: DengXian;background: white\">月由于原油出口减少，加拿大的出口下滑了</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;background: white\">2.9%</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: DengXian;background: white\">，而进口也下滑了</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;background: white\">0.5%</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: DengXian;background: white\">。</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: Verdana, sans-serif\"><br/> <br/> </span><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190111/1547148209299682.jpg\" title=\"1547148209299682.jpg\" alt=\"0004.jpg\"/></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: DengXian;background: white\">不利的统计数据虽然造成加元昨天曾短暂下跌，但由于国际油价的上涨，加元昨天全天依然上涨。</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: Verdana, sans-serif\"><br/> <br/> </span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: DengXian;background: white\">加元在去年可谓跌跌不休，加元兑美元汇率下跌近</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;background: white\">8</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: DengXian;background: white\">％。</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: Verdana, sans-serif\"><br/> <br/> </span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: DengXian;background: white\">特别是第四季度最为恶劣，</span> <span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: DengXian;background: white\">自</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;background: white\">10</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: DengXian;background: white\">月以来暴跌近</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;background: white\">6</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: DengXian;background: white\">％。</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: Verdana, sans-serif\"><br/> <br/> </span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: DengXian;background: white\">加拿大帝国商业银行（</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;background: white\">CIBC</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: DengXian;background: white\">）表示去年第</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;background: white\">4</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: DengXian;background: white\">季度，加元成为全球兑美元汇率表现第二差的主要货币，仅次于挪威克朗</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif;background: white\">。</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: DengXian;background: white\">加元最近一周的上涨已经挽回了去年下跌的部分损失。</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: Verdana, sans-serif\"><br/> <br/> </span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: DengXian;background: white\">此外，央行做出比加息决定取决于对加拿大经济形势的判断。</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: Verdana, sans-serif\"><br/> <br/> </span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: DengXian;background: white\">对于</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;background: white\">2019</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: DengXian;background: white\">年的各方面经济形势，加拿大央行预测：</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: Verdana, sans-serif\"><br/> <br/> </span><strong><span style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:107%;font-family:DengXian;color:red;background:white\">全球经济增长继续放缓</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: Verdana, sans-serif\"><br/> <br/> </span></p><p><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190111/1547148245856719.jpg\" title=\"1547148245856719.jpg\" alt=\"0005.jpg\"/></p><p><span style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:107%;font-family:DengXian;color:black;background:white\">预计</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:107%;font-family:&#39;Verdana&#39;,sans-serif;color:black;background:white\">2019</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:107%;font-family:DengXian;color:black;background:white\">年的全球经济的增长率将从之前预测的</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:107%;font-family:&#39;Verdana&#39;,sans-serif;color:black;background:white\">3.7</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:107%;font-family:DengXian;color:black;background:white\">％降至</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:107%;font-family:&#39;Verdana&#39;,sans-serif;color:black;background:white\">3.4</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:107%;font-family:DengXian;color:black;background:white\">％。特别是，</span><a href=\"http://www.westca.com/News/tags/tag=%C3%C0%B9%FA/lang=schinese.html?utm_source=westca&utm_medium=tag&utm_campaign=news_extend\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:107%;font-family:DengXian;color:#000099;background:white\">美国</span></a><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height:107%;font-family:DengXian;color:black;background:white\">的增长仍然稳固，但预计到</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:107%;font-family:&#39;Verdana&#39;,sans-serif;color:black;background:white\">2019</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height:107%;font-family:DengXian;color:black;background:white\">年将放缓至更可持续的步伐。但是越来越多的迹象表明，美中贸易冲突正在对全球需求和商品价格构成压力</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:107%;font-family:&#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;,sans-serif;color:black;background:white\">。</span></p><p><strong><span style=\"font-size:14px;line-height: 107%;font-family:DengXian;color:red;background:white\">石油价格下</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:107%;font-family:&#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;,sans-serif;color:red;background:white\">降</span></strong></p><p><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190111/1547148303278442.jpg\" title=\"1547148303278442.jpg\" alt=\"0006.jpg\"/><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190111/1547148308410369.jpg\" title=\"1547148308410369.jpg\" alt=\"0007.jpg\"/></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: DengXian;background: white\">全球石油基准价格比</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;background: white\">10</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: DengXian;background: white\">月货币政策报告预测的价格低了近</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;background: white\">25</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: DengXian;background: white\">％。全球油价下跌对加拿大经济前景产生重大影响，直接导致贸易和国民收入下降。</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: Verdana, sans-serif\"><br/> <br/> </span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: DengXian;background: white\">此外，运输限制和产量增加共同推高了加拿大西部的石油库存，并对加拿大基准价格施加了更大的下行压力</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif;background: white\">。</span></p><p><strong><span style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:107%;font-family: DengXian;color:red;background:white\">就业率高工资增长低</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:107%;font-family:&#39;Verdana&#39;,sans-serif;color:red;background:white\">&nbsp;</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:107%;font-family:DengXian;color:red;background:white\">加元走低</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: Verdana, sans-serif\"><br/> <br/> </span></p><p><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190111/1547148385566741.jpg\" title=\"1547148385566741.jpg\" alt=\"0008.jpg\"/></p><p><span style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:107%;font-family:DengXian;color:black;background:white\">尽管加拿大就业增长强劲，失业率处于</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height:107%;font-family:&#39;Verdana&#39;,sans-serif;color:black;background:white\">40</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;line-height: 107%;font-family:DengXian;color:black;background:white\">年来的最低点，但雇员工资增长缓慢。加元在</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:107%;font-family:&#39;Verdana&#39;,sans-serif;color:black;background:white\">2019</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height:107%;font-family:DengXian;color:black;background:white\">年预计将走低</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:107%;font-family:&#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;,sans-serif;color:black;background:white\">。</span></p><p><strong><span style=\"font-size:14px;line-height: 107%;font-family:DengXian;color:red;background:white\">房</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height:107%;font-family:&#39;Verdana&#39;,sans-serif;color:red;background:white\"><a href=\"http://www.westca.com/News/tags/tag=%B5%D8%B2%FA/lang=schinese.html?utm_source=westca&utm_medium=tag&utm_campaign=news_extend\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-family:DengXian;color:#000099\">地产</span></a></span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:107%;font-family:DengXian;color:red;background:white\">市场减</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:107%;font-family:&#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;,sans-serif;color:red;background:white\">缓</span></strong></p><p><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190111/1547148401168273.jpg\" title=\"1547148401168273.jpg\" alt=\"0009.jpg\"/></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: DengXian;background: white\">央行的贷款政策和</span><span style=\"font-size:15px;line-height:107%;font-family:&#39;Calibri&#39;,sans-serif\"><a href=\"http://www.westca.com/News/tags/tag=%C0%FB%C2%CA/lang=schinese.html?utm_source=westca&utm_medium=tag&utm_campaign=news_extend\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:107%;font-family:DengXian;color:#000099;background:white\">利率</span></a></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: DengXian;background: white\">上升，与各级政府对</span><span style=\"font-size:15px;line-height:107%;font-family:&#39;Calibri&#39;,sans-serif\"><a href=\"http://www.westca.com/News/tags/tag=%B7%BF%B5%D8%B2%FA/lang=schinese.html?utm_source=westca&utm_medium=tag&utm_campaign=news_extend\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:107%;font-family:DengXian;color:#000099;background:white\">房地产</span></a></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: DengXian;background: white\">市场的调控政策共同影响下，房地产市场持全国主要城市都在续减弱，央行将继续监测</span><span style=\"font-size:15px;line-height:107%;font-family:&#39;Calibri&#39;,sans-serif\"><a href=\"http://www.westca.com/News/tags/tag=%B7%BF%CA%D0/lang=schinese.html?utm_source=westca&utm_medium=tag&utm_campaign=news_extend\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:107%;font-family:DengXian;color:#000099;background:white\">房市</span></a></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: DengXian;background: white\">的调整。</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: Verdana, sans-serif\"><br/> <br/> </span><strong><span style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:107%;font-family:&#39;Verdana&#39;,sans-serif;color:red;background:white\">GDP</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:107%;font-family:DengXian;color:red;background:white\">增长放缓</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: Verdana, sans-serif\"><br/> <img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190111/1547148468583007.jpg\" title=\"1547148468583007.jpg\" alt=\"00010.jpg\"/> <br/> </span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: Verdana, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: DengXian;background: white\">加拿大央行预测</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;background: white\">2019</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: DengXian;background: white\">年的</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;background: white\">GDP</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: DengXian;background: white\">国内生产总值将增长</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;background: white\">1.7</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: DengXian;background: white\">％，比</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;background: white\">10</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: DengXian;background: white\">月份的预测减少了</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;background: white\">0.4</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: DengXian;background: white\">个百分点。修订后的预测反映了</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;background: white\">2018</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: DengXian;background: white\">年第四季度和</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;background: white\">2019</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: DengXian;background: white\">年第一季度的暂时放缓。</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: Verdana, sans-serif\"><br/> <br/> </span><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190111/1547148482607940.jpg\" title=\"1547148482607940.jpg\" alt=\"00011.jpg\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: Verdana, sans-serif\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom:0;margin-bottom:0;line-height: normal\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;,sans-serif;color:black;background:white\">与之前预期一致。但由于原油价格下降，预计</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;Verdana&#39;,sans-serif;color:black;background:white\">CPI</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;,sans-serif;color:black;background:white\">通胀预计将进一步下滑并在</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;Verdana&#39;,sans-serif;color:black;background:white\">2019</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;,sans-serif;color:black;background:white\">年的大部分时间内低于</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;Verdana&#39;,sans-serif;color:black;background:white\">2</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;,sans-serif;color:black;background:white\">％。另一方面，加元的较低水平将对通胀施加一些上行压力。</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;font-family:&#39;Verdana&#39;,sans-serif;color:black\"><br/> <br/> <span style=\"background:white\">2018</span></span><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;,sans-serif;color:black;background:white\">年三四季度时，业内普遍认为加息将是</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;Verdana&#39;,sans-serif;color:black;background:white\">2019</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;,sans-serif;color:black;background:white\">年的主旋律，</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;,serif\"><a href=\"http://www.westca.com/News/tags/tag=%B4%FB%BF%EE%C0%FB%C2%CA/lang=schinese.html?utm_source=westca&utm_medium=tag&utm_campaign=news_extend\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;,sans-serif;color:#000099;background:white\">贷款利率</span></a></span><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;,sans-serif;color:black;background:white\">也会随之继续上涨。</span></p><p><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190111/1547148527316162.jpg\" title=\"1547148527316162.jpg\" alt=\"00012.jpg\"/><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: Verdana, sans-serif\"></span><br/></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: DengXian;background: white\">据介绍，在保持了近</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;background: white\">10</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: DengXian;background: white\">年的低</span><a href=\"http://www.westca.com/News/tags/tag=%C0%FB%C2%CA/lang=schinese.html?utm_source=westca&utm_medium=tag&utm_campaign=news_extend\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:107%;font-family:DengXian;color:#000099;background:white\">利率</span></a><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: DengXian;background: white\">政策后，自</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;background: white\">2017</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: DengXian;background: white\">年</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;background: white\">7</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: DengXian;background: white\">月开始，加拿大央行开始逐步加息</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif;background: white\">。</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: DengXian;background: white\">此前</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;background: white\">2009</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 107%;font-family: DengXian;background: wh