olor: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">温哥华排名第一$3230</p><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, 宋体; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">多伦多排名第二$2850</p><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, 宋体; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">本拿比排名第三$2290</p><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, 宋体; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">三睡房的呢，更不用看了</p><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, 宋体; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">靠北，谁租的起</p><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, 宋体; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">想当年两房一卫浴在列治文</p><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, 宋体; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">房租也才$1400！！！</p><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, 宋体; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">2019年1月详细数据</p><p><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190117/1547671408277740.jpg\" title=\"1547671408277740.jpg\" alt=\"3.jpg\" width=\"926\" height=\"620\" style=\"width: 926px; height: 620px;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, 宋体; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">其他城市也